Sixty-ninth Legislative Assembly of North Dakota
In Regular Session Commencing Tuesday, January 7, 2025
HOUSE BILL NO. 1077
(Government and Veterans Affairs Committee)
(At the request of the Adjutant General)
AN ACT to amend and reenact subsection 11 of section 54-52-01 of the North Dakota Century Code,
relating to the definition of national guard security officer and firefighter.
BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY OF NORTH DAKOTA:
SECTION 1. AMENDMENT. Subsection 11 of section 54-52-01 of the North Dakota Century Code
is amended and reenacted as follows:
11. "National guard security officer or firefighter" means a participating member who is:
a. A security police employee of the North Dakota national guard; or
b. A security officer employee of the North Dakota national guard; or
c. A firefighter employee of the North Dakota national guard.

